snippet: Transocean shareholders also backed one of Carl C. Icahn’s director nominees, though stockholders decided against his proposal for a $4 dividend.
abstract: Transocean shareholders vote out oil drilling company chairman J Michael Talbert; back one of Carl C Icahn's director nominees.
lead_paragraph: Transocean shareholders also backed one of Carl C. Icahn’s director nominees, though stockholders decided against his proposal for a $4 dividend.

headline.main: Icahn Wins Ouster of Transocean Chairman
